[101163224290756387441,100239417392589917824,When I was there last week they had superb happy hour cocktails which we then followed up with dinner and more drinks. I had the lamb risotto that was an ecstasy in every mouthful. The only quibble I had was their inability to split a cheque. We were a group of 12 and they couldn't break a bill. to be fair, it seemed to be a common malady in Portland.]
